<html lang='en'>

    <head>
        <meta charset='UTF-8' />
        <meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge' />
        <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
        <title>Email OTP</title>

    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        body {
            align-items: justify;
            margin: auto;
            width: 600px;
            height: 900px;
            font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .header_email {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: url('https://kalla-superapp-dev.s3.amazonaws.com/1654571788853-bg_header.png');
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        
        .otp {
            display: flex;
            max-width: 190px;
            height: 80px;
            background-color: #01803c;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            align-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        h2 {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        p {
            max-width: 552px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #111827;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        
        .safe {
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        span {
            color: #01803c;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        footer {
            margin-top: 35px;
        }
        
        .cust {
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        ul li {
            list-style-type: none;
            margin-left: -40px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
    </style>
    </head>

    <body>
        <header>
            <div class='header_email'>
                <img
                    src='https://kalla-superapp-dev.s3.amazonaws.com/1654571735517-logo_header.png'
                    alt='logo kalla'
                />
            </div>
        </header>

        <main>
            <div class='content'>
                <h2>Halo, {{member.name}}</h2>
                <p>
                    Silakan masukkan OTP ini untuk melanjutkan transaksi Anda di
                    Kalla Friends:
                </p>
                <div class='otp'>
                    <h2>{{otp}}</h2>
                </div>

                <p>Kode ini berlaku selama 10 Menit</p>

                <p class='safe'>
                    Jaga keamanan akun Anda dengan
                    <span>tidak membagikan OTP kepada siapa pun,</span>
                    termasuk staff Kalla Care. Terima kasih telah menggunakan
                    aplikasi Kalla Friend.
                </p>
            </div>
        </main>

        <footer>
            <img
                src='https://kalla-superapp-dev.s3.amazonaws.com/1654571767963-logo_footer.png'
                alt='logo kalla'
            />
            <p class='cust'>Customer Support</p>
            <ul>
                <li>WA : +62 811-4414-030</li>
                <li>Telp: 0411 3000 103</li>
                <li>Email: halo@kallafriends.com</li>
            </ul>
        </footer>
    </body>

</html>